manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: This exquisite notebook is an ideal tool for journaling or jotting down notes during college classes or office meetings.Crafted from premium quality leather, the soft cover lends it a refined look that is perfect for both academic and professional settings. The hardcover design ensures durability, with double-stitching providing additional reinforcement for long-lasting use.Whether you need a reliable companion for your academic pursuits or professional endeavors, this notebook is sure to exceed your expectations.

Comfortable Softcover Experience unparalleled comfort with this exceptional flat pack notebook. Featuring a soft cover design, it offers a superior writing experience, while the 180° flat lay enables effortless reading and efficient note-taking. The retro print design both unique and stylish, with a Nordic theme that covers the entire notebook, making it the perfect choice for special occasions such as back-to-school season, graduation season, Christmas, and birthdays. The exquisite bookmarks added convenience and enhance the notebook's efficiency, making it easier for you to flip through pages quickly. The 300 pages high quality thick journal boasts 150 sheets/300 pages, making it thicker than many other journals and providing ample space for you to express your thoughts. The 80gsm acid-free thick paper ensures smooth writing with no ink bleed, while the clean writing space delivers a pleasant journaling experience.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Elegant and timeless
reviews.reviewText: As an avid writer and stationery enthusiast, I recently acquired a stunning leather journal that has quickly become one of my most prized possessions. Crafted with precision and elegance, this journal embodies the perfect marriage of form and function, making it an absolute delight to use.The first thing that struck me upon receiving the journal was its exquisite craftsmanship. The supple, genuine leather cover exudes a rich, earthy aroma and a luxurious feel, attesting to the high quality of materials used. The tactile experience of running my fingers over the smooth, grainy surface is truly satisfying, and the journal's sturdiness promises to protect my thoughts and musings for years to come.Upon opening its pages, I was greeted by thick, cream-colored, acid-free paper that is an absolute joy to write on. The paper's weight and texture lend themselves perfectly to a variety of writing instruments, from fountain pens to pencils, and even watercolors. The faint, inviting scent of the paper adds to the overall sensory experience of using this journal.What truly sets this leather journal apart, however, is its thoughtful design. The binding allows the journal to lie flat, making it effortless to write across the entire page. Additionally, a built-in bookmark ensures that I can easily locate my most recent entries, while the elastic closure keeps the journal securely shut when not in use. Finally, the journal's generous size provides ample space for my thoughts and creativity to flourish.In conclusion, this leather journal is a testament to classic elegance and functionality. It exudes a timeless appeal that is sure to captivate any discerning writer or artist. Whether as a personal indulgence or a thoughtful gift for a kindred spirit, this journal is a treasure that I wholeheartedly recommend. With its impeccable craftsmanship and attention to detail, it has undoubtedly earned its place as an essential companion in my creative journey.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I knew I would like this notebook but as soon as I had it in my hands, I was in love with it. The cover is absolutely gorgeous and flexible. Love the fact that is 180°, so it's always easy to write on the pages. The paper is really good as well. I bought it for tarot journaling and it's perfect! Good price, great quality, amazing aesthetics.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I really love this journal. The texture of the fake leather is very satisfying. I like the quality of the paper, it feels great to write notes on. I take this journal with me in my bag, super useful!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I am a daily journal writer and wanted to get something a little more stylish than my previous journals and found this one on Amazon. I made sure the size would match my other journals and fit in my bookshelf with all of the others. Everything looked good and so I ordered it. When it came I noticed that there are only 21 lines per page instead of the usual 26 I prefer. It is a little thing but something I am very particular about. I will gift it to someone instead of use it myself as I feel that is a great price for the product and don't want to return it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well organized and professional
reviews.reviewText: I usually struggle with keeping a journal, but this one helps keep me on track. It certainly seems to be intended for professional use but I use it as my personal keep. There’s spaces for just about any average note such as date, memo #, and even weather for the day. Feels good to hold and has an appealing look to it with a well made design. It doesn’t feel cheap and seems sturdy enough. Would definitely recommend.
